7.1 Empty statement
===================

There is an empty statement in Dino.  It denotes no action.  The empty
statement is included in Dino for convenience.

               ExecutiveStmt = ";"

   Example: Usage of an empty statement in a for-statement:

               for (i = 0; a[i] == 0; i++)
                 ;


